{"id":630772,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/【图说天朝】赵国的特色官威-从学生会开始/","date":"2019-12-21T03:44:04Z","modified":"2019-12-21T03:44:04Z","title":"【图说天朝】赵国的特色官威 从学生会开始","content":"<p>近日，互联网上又有大学“特色官威”聊天截图流出：一名学生会“副部长”因为后辈未称呼其职务而“耍官威”拒看邮件。不过令人意外的是，这名后辈却“愤怒回怼”，极有性格，让不少网友叫好。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWU0AA1Gxr.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-630773\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWU0AA1Gxr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWU0AA1Gxr.jpeg 302w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWU0AA1Gxr-252x300.jpeg 252w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUYAAj6Di.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-630775\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUYAAj6Di.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUYAAj6Di.jpeg 295w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUYAAj6Di-246x300.jpeg 246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulYVUAAB9q6.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-630776\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulYVUAAB9q6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulYVUAAB9q6.jpeg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulYVUAAB9q6-300x192.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUEAAMJt9.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-630774\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUEAAMJt9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUEAAMJt9.jpeg 295w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMlulWUEAAMJt9-246x300.jpeg 246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>事件后续：</strong>“副部长”男友要求该名学生道歉，再度引发“战斗”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1CUwAAoh6Q.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-630777\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1CUwAAoh6Q.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1CUwAAoh6Q.jpeg 506w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1CUwAAoh6Q-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1DU0AA3kEK.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-630778\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1DU0AA3kEK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1DU0AA3kEK.jpeg 506w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/EMMmC1DU0AA3kEK-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"rkcoFFIqTy\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%9d%a8%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%ad%e6%98%af%e4%bd%a0%e4%bb%ac%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5-%e7%9a%84%ef%bc%9f/\">【图说天朝】杨主席是你们直接 @的？（后续）</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【图说天朝】杨主席是你们直接 @的？（后续）》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e6%9d%a8%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%ad%e6%98%af%e4%bd%a0%e4%bb%ac%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5-%e7%9a%84%ef%bc%9f/embed/#?secret=rkcoFFIqTy\" data-secret=